high_descs: walk around and watching the room
pick up the cloth in the bed
exit the room to reach the sink.
Clean the cloth in the sink and take another cloth.
Place the cloth on the toilet near the sink.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the cloth in bed and place the cloth on the near toilet

high_descs: Turn to the right. Approach the bed.
Leave the room. Turn left. Go forward and then to the right. Go into the bathroom and go to the sink.
Place the cloth to the left of the sink and open the faucets for 4 seconds. Grab the rag.
Turn right. Go ahead, turn right and turn left.  Raise the rag.
Place the cloth on the left side, at the end of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Find a cloth. Place it over a toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the bed.
Take the cloth from the bed.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the cloth into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go near the toilet.
Put the cloth on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cloth on the toilet.
